{"id":87,"idInBook":221,"chapterId":4,"bookId":1,"arabic":"حَدَّثَنَا عَبْدَانُ، قَالَ أَخْبَرَنَا عَبْدُ اللَّهِ، قَالَ أَخْبَرَنَا يَحْيَى بْنُ سَعِيدٍ، قَالَ سَمِعْتُ أَنَسَ بْنَ مَالِكٍ، عَنِ النَّبِيِّ صلى الله عليه وسلم‏.‏","english":{"narrator":"Narrated Anas bin Malik:","text":"The Prophet (ﷺ) said as above (219)."},"hadithNumber":221,"vol":1,"hadithId":87,"reference":"4:87","meta":{"id":"bukhari","length":7563,"totalChapters":97,"arabic":{"title":"صحيح البخاري","author":"الإمام محمد بن إسماعيل البخاري"},"english":{"title":"Sahih Al Bukhari","author":"Imam Muhammad ibn Ismail al-Bukhari"}},"chapter":{"id":4,"bookId":1,"arabic":"كتاب الوضوء","english":"Ablutions (Wudu')","startHadith":135,"endHadith":247,"totalHadiths":113},"version":{"name":"bukhari","title":"Sahih Al Bukhari","chapters":97}}